snippet: Quarterback Zach Mettenberger looked nonchalant behind Louisiana State’s offensive line, helping the Tigers dismantle Washington in the team’s 39th consecutive nonconference win.
abstract: Louisiana State crushes Washington, 41-3, in college football action.
lead_paragraph: Quarterback Zach Mettenberger looked nonchalant behind Louisiana State’s offensive line, helping the Tigers dismantle Washington in the team’s 39th consecutive nonconference win.
